<statement>
<p>
A population of bacteria is growing according to the equation <m>\displaystyle{P}{\left({t}\right)}={700}{e}^{{{0.19}{t}}}</m>.  Estimate when the population will exceed 1286.</p>
<p>
<em>t</em>= <fillin characters="20" /> Â  </p>
<p>
